description: Updates a key group. When you update a key group, all the fields are updated with the values provided in the request. You cannot update some fields independent of others. To update a key group:

parameters.name: KeyGroupConfig
parameters.description: The key group configuration. A name to identify the key group. A list of the identifiers of the public keys in the key group. (string) --- Comment (string) --- A comment to describe the key group. The comment cannot be longer than 128 characters.

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: A name to identify the key group.

nested_params.name: Items
nested_params.description: A list of the identifiers of the public keys in the key group.

nested_params.name: Comment
nested_params.description: A comment to describe the key group. The comment cannot be longer than 128 characters.

parameters.name: Id
parameters.description: The identifier of the key group that you are updating.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The identifier for the key group.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time when the key group was last modified.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: A name to identify the key group.

nested_items.name: Items
nested_items.description: A list of the identifiers of the public keys in the key group.

nested_items.name: Comment
nested_items.description: A comment to describe the key group. The comment cannot be longer than 128 characters.

nested_items.name: ETag
nested_items.description: The identifier for this version of the key group.
